### API Testing Definitions for Inventory Management

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/v1

### 1. Ktra Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Accept: application/json

### 2. Device Registry: Tạo mới thiết bị
POST {{baseUrl}}/devices
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "device_id": "SCALE-001",
  "name": "Cân Nhập Kho 01",
  "sku_code": "SKU-500KG",
  "status": "active"
}

### 3. Device Registry: Lấy danh sách thiết bị
GET {{baseUrl}}/devices
Accept: application/json

### 4. Device Registry: Lấy thông tin thiết bị theo ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/devices/SCALE-001
Accept: application/json

### 5. Calibration Manager: Tạo cấu hình Calibration mới
POST {{baseUrl}}/devices/SCALE-001/calibration
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "zero_value": 0.05,
  "span_value": 500.0,
  "unit": "kg",
  "capacity_max": 1000.0,
  "hardware_config": {
    "adc_rate": 80,
    "filter_type": "moving_average",
    "sample_count": 10
  },
  "created_by": "admin"
}

### 6. Calibration Manager: Lấy cấu hình Active hiện tại
GET {{baseUrl}}/devices/SCALE-001/calibration/active
Accept: application/json
